      <body>I have the same problem:

 undefined method `error_message' for #&lt;ActionView::Helpers::InstanceTag:0x40be40c&gt;

Looking at the code (both Rails-3.0.0.beta and Edge in GitHub) at the bottom of active_model_helper.rb (http://github.com/rails/rails/blob/master/actionpack/lib/action_view/helpers/active_model_helper.rb) you can see that ActiveRecordInstanceTag has not that method defined.

I have prepared a patch which fixes the omission and includes a test.</body>
